OL,6,FPathologist Dr Kirsten Hope said she
OL,7,Ffound 15 stab wounds and at least 11
OL,8,Fslash wounds on her face, body and
OL,9,Farms.
OL,11,FDr Hope said some of the injuries to
OL,12,FMs Akter's arm and hand appeared to be
OL,13,Fdefensive injuries which happened as
OL,14,Fshe tried to protect her face from the
OL,15,Fweapon.
OL,17,FThe jury was told Ms Akter's death was
OL,18,Fcaused by a wound to her neck. It
OL,19,Fpenetrated her windpipe and the
OL,20,Fjugular vein in her neck which led to
OL,21,Fmassive blood loss.
